description: Gwen, Spot, and Horatio are trapped underground with a horde of zombies – and unlike Gwen, these are the shambling, feast-on-the-flesh-of-the-living kind! Meanwhile, Gramps the Chimp sets out to find his lost grandson, Amon and Ellie make a startling discovery, and when The Dead Presidents arrive, things get very complicated for everyone's favorite zombie girl detective.
name: Rising

description: A sort of irresistible force obliges the two mortal enemies Martin Mystère and Sergej Orloff to gather in the forgotten monastery of Taglakhar, "the castle on the cliff", located in a remote area of the Himalayas. Here, the wise Kut Humi recalls for the two rivals a past of serene friendship, that Mystère and Orloff revive in the quiet mystique of the "roof of the world" ..
name: Il presagio

description: An invisible realm vigils over the fate of humanity since its origins : it is Agarthi , the nerve center of the energies of the planet . But Agarthi is in danger , its survival is linked to the Holy Grail , that was kept there , and that was stolen by an explorer on a mission on behalf of Hitler . Kut Humi entrusts to his disciples Mystere and Orloff the task to recover it.
name: Agarthi!

description:
The miniseries that leads into the video game continues under the guidance of game writer Paul Dini. The gates swing shut on Arkham City, trapping small-time criminals and deadly Super-Villains behind its walls. As the prisoners struggle for survival, a rogue unit of Mayor Sharp's security force hunts down rival gang bosses The Joker and Two-Face. Not only must Batman save the lives of his greatest foes, he's got to fight his way through an army to do it!

Batman escapes Hugo Strange's trap with the aid of Catwoman while the Joker has a pleasant visit from his doctor.
name: A Night on the Town
